 <i>that whenever</i>
 <i>she sprayed water</i>

00:15:53.020 --> 00:15:54.955 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>all over Gunpei's body,</i>

00:15:57.024 --> 00:15:59.426 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>somehow, his skin would</i>
 <i>temporarily return</i>

00:15:59.460 --> 00:16:02.329 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>to the state it was in</i>
 <i>when he was alive.</i>

00:16:04.198 --> 00:16:06.935 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're so cute
when you're asleep,

00:16:06.967 --> 00:16:10.270 position:16% line:83% align:start
Gunpei, and you are mine
and mine alone.

00:16:11.271 --> 00:16:13.307 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm the only person
in the whole world

00:16:13.340 --> 00:16:16.176 position:24% line:83% align:start
who could take care
of you forever and ever.

00:16:17.177 --> 00:16:19.046 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Rohan]W <i>hat exactly is he?</i>

00:16:19.079 --> 00:16:22.382 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's no denying he's been</i>
 <i>dead this entire time.</i>

00:16:24.519 --> 00:16:26.855 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I first learned of</i>
 <i>Gunpei Kamafusa</i>

00:16:26.888 --> 00:16:28.790 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>on one of my trips</i>
 <i>to the area.</i>

00:16:28.823 --> 00:16:30.257 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>His name arose</i>
 <i>while I was talking</i>

00:16:30.290 --> 00:16:32.927 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>to some Mutsukabe villagers</i>
 <i>about their stories</i>

00:16:32.961 --> 00:16:36.096 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and long-held beliefs</i>
 <i>in local monsters.</i>

00:16:36.129 --> 00:16:38.131 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Batsudera]
So, you see, Mr. Kashibe,

00:16:38.165 --> 00:16:41.201 position:19% line:83% align:start
this is an absolutely,
positively, fantastic,

00:16:41.235 --> 00:16:43.905 position:16% line:83% align:start
profitable and lucrative
deal for you.

00:16:43.938 --> 00:16:45.740 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
Absolutely not.

00:16:45.773 --> 00:16:47.074 position:33% line:83% align:start
I've told you
a hundred times,

00:16:47.107 --> 00:16:48.375 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm not selling my hills.

00:16:48.408 --> 00:16:49.944 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well, I'm sure
there's some way

00:16:49.978 --> 00:16:51.579 position:35% line:83% align:start
we can help
change your mind.

00:16:51.613 --> 00:16:53.515 position:35% line:89% align:start
(chuckles)

00:16:53.548 --> 00:16:54.516 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:54.949 --> 00:16:56.183 position:44% line:89% align:start
Oh...

00:16:56.216 --> 00:16:58.385 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Batsudera] Yes, hello?
This is Batsudera...

00:16:59.286 --> 00:17:01.523 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
 <i>I learned of this affair</i>

00:17:01.556 --> 00:17:03.691 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>when I stumbled into</i>
 <i>a chance encounter</i>

00:17:03.725 --> 00:17:05.392 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>with Naoko Osito</i>

00:17:05.425 --> 00:17:08.362 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and read her memory</i>
 <i>with Heaven's Door.</i>

00:17:08.395 --> 00:17:10.097 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's through</i>
 <i>this stroke of luck</i>

00:17:10.130 --> 00:17:14.268 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>that I learned about</i>
 <i>the existence of this...man.</i>

00:17:14.301 --> 00:17:17.070 position:38% line:83% align:start
Yes? Huh?
Hey, can you hear me?

00:17:17.104 --> 00:17:19.406 position:27% line:83% align:start
The signal's bad.
Just a moment please.

00:17:20.274 --> 00:17:23.377 position:21% line:83% align:start
So, what are you...?
Huh, Gunpei?

00:17:23.410 --> 00:17:26.614 position:16% line:83% align:start
I intend to see the truth
with my own two eyes.

00:17:27.649 --> 00:17:28.683 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
I want to know

00:17:29.617 --> 00:17:30.718 position:24% line:89% align:start
what you're after.

00:17:32.152 --> 00:17:33.755 position:33% line:83% align:start
In the attic
above the closet

00:17:33.788 --> 00:17:35.023 position:24% line:89% align:start
in that main house,

00:17:35.055 --> 00:17:36.390 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll find him there.

00:17:36.423 --> 00:17:38.793 position:10% line:83% align:start
[girl] You're Rohan Kishibe,
aren't you?

00:17:38.826 --> 00:17:40.060 position:27% line:89% align:start
The manga artist?

00:17:40.929 --> 00:17:42.362 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's what I thought.

00:17:42.396 --> 00:17:45.065 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'd heard you'd been
snooping around here lately.

00:17:46.099 --> 00:17:47.467 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
Who are you?

00:17:47.502 --> 00:17:50.838 position:13% line:83% align:start
My family always warned me
not to talk to strange men.

00:17:52.272 --> 00:17:54.207 position:21% line:83% align:start
Apparently, there are
a lot of perverts

00:17:54.241 --> 00:17:56.109 position:35% line:83% align:start
and weirdos
around these days.

00:17:57.512 --> 00:17:58.345 position:41% line:83% align:start
[girl]
(grunts)

00:17:58.378 --> 00:17:59.079 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:17:59.112 --> 00:18:00.480 position:21% line:89% align:start
Wait, what are you-?

00:18:00.515 --> 00:18:03.116 position:30% line:89% align:start
(intense music)

00:18:03.918 --> 00:18:05.118 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:08.056 --> 00:18:11.258 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, are you all right?
What was all that about?

00:18:11.926 --> 00:18:12.827 position:16% line:89% align:start
Running off like that...

00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:14.328 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasp)

00:18:15.095 --> 00:18:17.230 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Rohan] <i>She... She's dead.</i>

00:18:17.899 --> 00:18:19.667 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>Wh...What happened?</i>

00:18:20.467 --> 00:18:21.536 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>It can't be!</i>

00:18:22.971 --> 00:18:25.238 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's absurd, ridiculous!</i>

00:18:26.074 --> 00:18:27.474 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>This makes it look like...</i>

00:18:28.943 --> 00:18:31.144 position:24% line:89% align:start
It looks like I...

00:18:31.178 --> 00:18:34.381 position:24% line:83% align:start
was responsible for
this poor girl's death!

00:18:34.414 --> 00:18:37.719 position:21% line:83% align:start
What's going on here?
Who the hell is this girl?

00:18:38.185 --> 00:18:39.353 position:30% line:89% align:start
It can't be...

00:18:39.386 --> 00:18:41.154 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
There's no way!

00:18:41.188 --> 00:18:44.157 position:33% line:83% align:start
Is this girl
Gunpei's child?

00:18:44.759 --> 00:18:46.027 position:30% line:89% align:start
Naoko Osito...

00:18:46.060 --> 00:18:48.029 position:21% line:89% align:start
did she get pregnant

00:18:48.062 --> 00:18:49.797 position:30% line:83% align:start
from the corpse
hiding in the attic,

00:18:49.831 --> 00:18:51.032 position:27% line:89% align:start
and give birth?!

00:18:51.065 --> 00:18:53.601 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Batsudera] Mr. Kishibe,
where are you?

00:18:53.635 --> 00:18:55.135 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
(gasps)

00:18:55.168 --> 00:18:58.305 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Batsudera] Where are you,
Mr. Kishibe?

00:18:59.574 --> 00:19:00.575 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

00:19:01.509 --> 00:19:02.677 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
(frustrated groan)

00:19:02.710 --> 00:19:05.613 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Rohan] <i>Damn it,</i>
 <i>it's trying to possess me!</i>

00:19:05.980 --> 00:19:06.748 position:41% line:89% align:start
(pulse)

00:19:06.781 --> 00:19:08.415 position:30% line:89% align:start
Heaven's Door!

00:19:08.448 --> 00:19:09.449 position:41% line:89% align:start
(blast)

00:19:11.284 --> 00:19:12.587 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
This is bad.

00:19:12.620 --> 00:19:15.222 position:21% line:83% align:start
All the memories that
make this girl who she is...

00:19:15.255 --> 00:19:16.891 position:21% line:89% align:start
They're fading away!

00:19:16.924 --> 00:19:18.760 position:41% line:83% align:start
No, no!
It's all disappearing!

00:19:18.793 --> 00:19:21.228 position:24% line:83% align:start
If her memories go,
I can't bring it back!

00:19:21.261 --> 00:19:22.496 position:24% line:89% align:start
So, before that...

00:19:23.865 --> 00:19:25.399 position:33% line:89% align:start
(scribbling)

00:19:25.900 --> 00:19:27.200 position:30% line:89% align:start
(booming noise)

00:19:27.234 --> 00:19:29.103 position:35% line:89% align:start
(cracking)

00:19:29.137 --> 00:19:31.204 position:41% line:83% align:start
[girl]
(groaning)

00:19:31.238 --> 00:19:34.509 position:27% line:83% align:start
-(intense noise)
-(scream)

00:19:34.542 --> 00:19:35.576 position:41% line:89% align:start
(grunt)

00:19:35.610 --> 00:19:42.215 position:33% line:89% align:start
(air gushing)

00:19:48.022 --> 00:19:49.957 position:35% line:89% align:start
(groaning)

00:19:49.991 --> 00:19:52.560 position:24% line:89% align:start
(confused groaning)

00:19:54.227 --> 00:19:55.596 position:24% line:89% align:start
(confused groaning)

00:19:56.798 --> 00:19:57.799 position:24% line:89% align:start
(confused groaning)

00:19:58.900 --> 00:20:02.637 position:30% line:83% align:start
[girl] (giggle)
Mom! I'm hungry!

00:20:03.905 --> 00:20:06.273 position:24% line:83% align:start
That was too close
for comfort.

00:20:06.306 --> 00:20:07.875 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Rohan]
A moment's hesitation,

00:20:07.909 --> 00:20:09.510 position:27% line:83% align:start
and I could have
been possessed.

00:20:11.112 --> 00:20:12.412 position:30% line:89% align:start
Or, worse yet,

00:20:13.246 --> 00:20:14.414 position:35% line:89% align:start
devastated.

00:20:15.116 --> 00:20:16.851 position:13% line:89% align:start
What a terrifying creature!

00:20:16.884 --> 00:20:18.218 position:27% line:89% align:start
Another second...

00:20:18.251 --> 00:20:20.955 position:24% line:83% align:start
Ah, so that's where
you went, Mr. Kishibe!

00:20:20.988 --> 00:20:23.891 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm terribly sorry to have
left you alone like that.

00:20:23.925 --> 00:20:25.026 position:16% line:89% align:start
It was an important call

00:20:25.059 --> 00:20:26.794 position:21% line:83% align:start
from the main office,
you see.

00:20:26.828 --> 00:20:28.896 position:19% line:83% align:start
You can take your offer
and shove it.

00:20:29.429 --> 00:20:30.732 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:20:30.765 --> 00:20:32.900 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Batsudera]
What...?!

00:20:32.934 --> 00:20:36.204 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Rohan] <i>This was</i>
 <i>the very monster I sought.</i>

00:20:36.236 --> 00:20:39.640 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll call it the monster</i>
 <i>of Mutsukabe Hill.</i>

00:20:39.674 --> 00:20:42.677 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I don't know how long</i>
 <i>this monster has existed.</i>

00:20:42.710 --> 00:20:43.811 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>Perhaps forever.</i>

00:20:43.845 --> 00:20:45.012 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>It preys on love,</i>

00:20:45.046 --> 00:20:46.881 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>and the human heart's</i>
 <i>weakness.</i>

00:20:46.914 --> 00:20:49.817 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>In doing so, it makes humans</i>
 <i>do everything for it.</i>

00:20:49.851 --> 00:20:52.319 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>It doesn't work,</i>
 <i>takes no responsibility,</i>

00:20:52.352 --> 00:20:53.821 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and suffers no hardship.</i>

00:20:55.288 --> 00:20:58.492 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>This monster's sole purpose</i>
 <i>is to reproduce.</i>

00:20:59.627 --> 00:21:02.697 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>No, perhaps I should</i>
 <i>call it an organism.</i>

00:21:03.898 --> 00:21:07.101 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>The greatest moment</i>
 <i>of this creature's life is</i>

00:21:07.135 --> 00:21:09.269 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>when it dies</i>
 <i>in front of someone.</i>

00:21:10.270 --> 00:21:11.873 position:30% line:83% align:start
I do think that
it's possible

00:21:11.906 --> 00:21:14.274 position:19% line:83% align:start
more of these creatures
are out there somewhere.

00:21:14.307 --> 00:21:16.244 position:27% line:83% align:start
They may prolong
their existence

00:21:16.276 --> 00:21:18.780 position:24% line:83% align:start
by finding a victim
to die in front of.

00:21:18.813 --> 00:21:21.249 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Koichi]
Is that really a true story?

00:21:21.281 --> 00:21:22.449 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's a hard pill
to swallow.

00:21:22.482 --> 00:21:23.618 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Okuyasu] Even so,
-(gasps)

00:21:23.651 --> 00:21:26.353 position:30% line:83% align:start
there's no way
that story's a complete lie.

00:21:26.386 --> 00:21:27.655 position:30% line:83% align:start
Have you heard
of this monster?

00:21:27.688 --> 00:21:29.857 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Mikitaka] Yes, I do
remember a similar creature

00:21:29.891 --> 00:21:32.359 position:16% line:83% align:start
that made its home among
the magellanic clouds.

00:21:32.392 --> 00:21:33.628 position:19% line:89% align:start
L-Listen up, you kids.

00:21:33.661 --> 00:21:35.495 position:30% line:83% align:start
You can't just
barge into our--

00:21:35.530 --> 00:21:36.463 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasp)

00:21:36.496 --> 00:21:37.965 position:35% line:83% align:start
By the way,
there's something

00:21:37.999 --> 00:21:38.933 position:24% line:83% align:start
I've always wanted
to ask you.

00:21:38.966 --> 00:21:40.902 position:21% line:83% align:start
Are you serious when
you say you're an alien?

00:21:40.935 --> 00:21:44.038 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh yes, I traveled
from the magellanic clouds

00:21:44.071 --> 00:21:45.673 position:19% line:89% align:start
to live here in Morio,

00:21:45.706 --> 00:21:47.175 position:27% line:83% align:start
but my spaceship
is still standing...

00:21:47.208 --> 00:21:48.441 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Okuyasu]
(growl)

00:21:48.475 --> 00:21:51.378 position:24% line:83% align:start
All this alien crap
is putting me to sleep here.

00:21:53.548 --> 00:21:55.315 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Rohan] <i>How many</i>
 <i>Mutsukabe Hills monsters</i>

00:21:55.348 --> 00:21:56.551 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>walk this world?</i>

00:21:56.584 --> 00:21:59.287 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I have no interest</i>
 <i>in questions like that.</i>

00:22:00.588 --> 00:22:03.257 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Naoko Osito</i>
 <i>looks happy enough,</i>

00:22:03.291 --> 00:22:05.492 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and I've discovered</i>
 <i>the monster's purpose.</i>

00:22:07.195 --> 00:22:08.596 position:27% line:89% align:start
I know what I am,

00:22:08.629 --> 00:22:11.464 position:19% line:83% align:start
and it's not a scholar,
or a journalist, either.

00:22:12.200 --> 00:22:15.102 position:47% line:83% align:start
Me?
I'm just a manga artist.

00:22:16.037 --> 00:22:17.038 position:41% line:83% align:start
[girl]
Mom!

00:22:18.973 --> 00:22:22.375 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you think I'll marry
a handsome man one day?

00:22:23.644 --> 00:22:24.979 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Naoko]
Of course, you will.

00:22:28.916 --> 00:22:33.888 position:21% line:89% align:start
(ending theme music)

